<h2> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+4">Menu-based Interaction -- Overview</font></font></h2>&nbsp; 
<h4> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+3">3 basic activities:</font></font></h4><ul> 
<li> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+2">Navigation (in menu hierarchy, 
information resource, etc.)</font></font></li><li> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+2">Selection 
(of data, parameters, etc.)</font></font></li><li> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+2">Activation 
(of programs, documents, etc.)</font></font></li></ul><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+3"><b>Selection 
made</b> </font><font size="+2">through mouse, number/character keys, function keys, 
cursor keys plus return key, rotating cursor symbol plus return key, touching 
on the screen, etc.</font></font> <br> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+2">Special 
case: "analog" menus </font></font><font><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="6"><a href="menu-types-examples.jpg"><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><a href="sliders.jpeg"><img style="border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;" src="../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif" alt="The linked image shows several types of &quot;analog&quot; slikders"></a></a></font></font></font> <h4> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+3">Types 
of menus </font><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="6"><a href="menu-types-examples.jpg"><img src="../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif" alt="The linked image shows several types of menus, namely textual menus, a menu that can be activated with function keys, a pulldown menu, and a graphical menu" border="0" height="11" width="11"></a></font></font></h4><ul> 
<li> <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+2">Textual menus</font></font></li><li> 
